data.description: Location Location! This 5 bedroom/ 3 full bathroom home boasts 3100 sq ft with side-loading 2-car garage is located in the Fairfield Community of Virginia Beach. 1st floor features hardwood flooring, formal living room, spacious dining room, an expansive kitchen featuring an oversized island with gas-burning cooktop & extra seating room, endless cabinetry and storage space, tile flooring & recessed lighting. Family room adorns floor-to-ceiling shelving w. storage space on both sides of the fireplace and French doors leading out to large sunroom (ft. some newly installed windows)! 2nd floor features hardwood flooring throughout & lots of natural lighting. The primary bedroom is quite spacious and offers a large walkin closet. Full exterior has just had a makeover to include painting of trim, doors, shutters & siding, gutters, windows & casings, garage doors and more! Fully-fenced in backyard offers an in-ground pool with New liner (4/24) and plenty of space! Schedule your tour today!
